${B}New here? Pick your path${R} — or run ${CY}rlm start${R} for guided setup:

${B}①  Build a brand-new org${R}  (you create your own scratch orgs)
  ${CY}rlm login --devhub${R}     Connect a Salesforce ${B}Dev Hub${R}
  ${CY}rlm build${R}              Create + fully configure a fresh org
  ${CY}rlm open${R}               Open it in your browser

${B}②  Customize an org you already have${R}  (sandbox / dev / existing scratch)
  ${CY}rlm login${R}              Connect that org   ${DIM}(add --sandbox for a sandbox)${R}
